  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting village children into school in Benin</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to get poor rural children cared for and into school. We have helped build classrooms and now have also completed and opened Chez Papa Geoff as a residential unit for needy orphaned and disabled children. Older children are sponsored into apprenticeships or further education. Purchasing land and providing agricultural equipment has been done to help the long-term sustainability of the project.</narrative>
  </description>
